PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?leader WHERE {
  fb:m.081pw fb:time.event.start_date ?start ; fb:time.event.end_date ?end .
  ?leader fb:government.politician.government_positions_held ?position .
  ?position fb:government.government_position_held.office_position_or_title fb:m.060d2 ; fb:government.government_position_held.from ?from ; fb:government.government_position_held.to ?to .
  FILTER ( ?from < ?end && ?to > ?start )
}

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?championship ?date WHERE {
  FILTER ( ?championship != fb:m.0jnq8 ) fb:m.0jnq8 fb:sports.sports_team.championships ?championship .
  ?championship fb:time.event.end_date ?date .
}
ORDER BY DESC ( ?date )
LIMIT 1
